text.tspan: Raven Figurine: becomes raven for 12h, can use Animal Msg spell on it
Misc: 5 magic arrows, backpack, bedroll, herbalism kit*, hide armor*,
mess kit, navigator's tools*, rations, 50' silk rope, shield*, waterskin
C - MAGIC STONE (BA, 1m): Turn <=3 pepples into magic range weapons - 1d6 + Mod
C - PRIMAL SAVAGERY (A): Melee spell attack within 5' - 2d10
C - PRODUCE FLAME (A, 10m): Create 10' bright + 10' dim light. Or attack 30' - 2d8
1 - ABSORB ELEMENT (R): Resist acid/cold/fire/lightning/thunder & +1d6 next melee
1 - ENTANGLEC (A, 1m): Difficult terrain in 20' sq w/i 90'. STR save or Restrained
1 - FAERIE FIREC (A, 1m): 20' cube w/i 60', DEX or outlined & face Adv on attacks
1 - HEALING WORD (BA): Regain 1d4 + Mod to creature w/i 60'
2 - HEAT METALC (A, 1m): A metal obj w/i 60' - 2d8 fire + (CON & drops) or DisAdv
2 - MOONBEAMC (A, 1m): 5'r 40'H fills w/dim light. 2d10 radiant or CON save for 1/2
2 - PASS W/O TRACEC (A, 1hr): all allies w/i 30' get +10 to Stealth checks
3 - CONJURE ANIMALSC (A, 1hr): 1,2, 4, or 8 beats totaling 2 CR
3 - DISPEL MAGIC (A): 1 target w/i 120', spell ends if < 4th or WIS check (DC = 10+lvl)
3 - SPEAK W/PLANTS (A, 10m): plants w/i 30' talk & follow commands. Switch terrain
3 - TIDAL WAVE (A): w/i 120' cause up to 30'Lx10'Hx1'T. 4d8 & prone or DEX for 1/2
3 - WATER BREATHINGR (A, 24hr): <= 10 allies w/i 30' breathe normal underwater
4 - CONFUSIONC (A, 1m): All things w/i 10'r w/i 90' WIS save or confused
Personality: Pack loyalty; suspicious of outsiders; calm
Mannerisms: pyro; lush; avoids paper or metal
Ideals: Naturalism is more important than almost all
Bonds: Mother's necklace; stolen by trader.
Flaws: Ruthless vs those upsetting my view of natural
balance. Loyalty is a two-edged sword
Ul while dad tutored bow & sword skills; she
betrayed her social caste being with him.
- Pregnant mother forced to leave Ulfaren for my
safety. With father they decided to travel and I was
born on a ship while sailing the Gold Sea.
- Younger twin (1b, 1g) siblings born 3 years later.
- At age 8, while voyaging on a merchant ship out of
Rium, the ship wrecked, drowning parents and the
younger brother. The ship wasn't fully sea-worthy
- Journeyed alone, with sister, to Vastwood to seek
out paternal grandparents. During journey, was
deceived and lost only token of parents still had, a
small necklace from mother she'd been wearing.
- Lives with grandparents, takes to druid study
- Picked by Enclave for observation mission, in Rium.
Forced back to sea to fulfill aspects of that mission
- Safety of the Vastwood - aware from mother's
life, that she may have to sacrifice her own
preferences in order to do what's needed for
DarkVision: Dim -> bright w/i 60' & dark -> dim
Fey Blood: Adv on charm saves; can't be put to sleep
Mighty Summon: all conjured beasts gain 2 HP/hd
Ship's Passage: $0 travel, but no time or route input
Totem: BA, conjure spirit w/i 60', casts 30'r aura, 1m
Bear: all allies get 5+L tHP & Adv on STR rolls
Hawk: use R to give attack Adv & Adv on Percept
Unicorn: Adv on detection & restore L HP to allies
Wood Speech: beasts understand me & vice versa
